{
  "stem": "20142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because not always they could get the news from BBC and print it, so there was some chance, sometimes three days, sometimes four days.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every-- every fourth day or every third day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the funny part, I would like to emphasize that I never met the man who interrogated me at the very first time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said to me that if I would be ever approached, to respond only to the name Tadk, which means T-A-D-K.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, that's how I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is a matter of fact that the girl that I knew was supervising this district or whatever, she once approached me asking me if I need any food and things like this, because there was a really harsh day of distributing all the bottles because of the interferences of German movements of soldiers and some other groups.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jadzia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know the-- spelled J-A-D-Z-I-A.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't even have contact with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just knew that wherever I'm going, under different dressing, she will be supervising it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some time, when I spotted for some movements, she would even dress as a-- a-- a nurse, and the next time she was dressed as a elderly lady.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just conducting her work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt quite comfortable when I knew that there was somebody around, of overlooking what was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a sort of protection of my own self.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then one day, during the raid-- accidentally raid-- I was caught in a raid and--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Germans closed some streets and tightened up the entrances to the streets, and people who were male, people had to go out to the streets and they put them on a wagon and brought them to [?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Aleja ?] Szucha.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
